---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import { ExternalLink } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About · electionwatch.et"
  description="About electionwatch.et: an independent open-data portal for Ethiopia's 7th General Election."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl mb-6">About</h1>
    <div
      class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-ew-text-dim leading-relaxed space-y-5"
    >
      <p>
        <strong class="text-ew-text">electionwatch.et</strong> is an independent,
        open data portal for Ethiopia&rsquo;s 7th General Election. It is not affiliated
        with the Ethiopian government, <a
          href="https://nebe.org.et/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"
          >NEBE<ExternalLink class="w-3 h-3" /></a
        >, or any political party.
      </p>
      <p>
        We collect publicly available material, structure it into citable
        datasets, and publish it for free. New datasets are added through the
        election cycle.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ew-text mt-10 mb-3">Datasets</h2>
      <p>
        Two are live: question-by-question analyses of every official debate
        broadcast, and consolidated position files for parties that have
        appeared in one. More are in progress.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ew-text mt-10 mb-3">Citations</h2>
      <p>
        Every record links to its primary source. Where claims are summarised
        automatically by a language model, the same link lets you check the
        model&rsquo;s work. Check the source before drawing conclusions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ew-text mt-10 mb-3">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Found an inaccuracy? Reach out to
        <a
          href="https://t.me/frectonz"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">@frectonz</a
        > on Telegram.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
